---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import HeaderEn from '../../components/HeaderEn.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <BaseHead
    title="Notary Public Ontario | Mandarin Notary Services | Miao He Law"
    description="Miao He is a commissioned Notary Public in Ontario. Notarization services in Mandarin and English for documents used in Canada and China. Markham. 647-930-6688."
  />
  <meta name="keywords" content="Notary Public Ontario Mandarin,Chinese notary public Toronto,notarize documents Ontario,Mandarin notary Markham,Chinese notary Mississauga,notary public GTA Chinese,notarize documents for China,Ontario notary public Chinese lawyer,certified true copy Ontario,statutory declaration Ontario Chinese" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="Notary Public Ontario | Mandarin | Miao He Law" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Commissioned Notary Public in Ontario. Mandarin and English notarization services for documents used in Canada and China. 647-930-6688." />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://www.miaohelaw.ca/en/notary-public" />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://www.miaohelaw.ca/en/notary-public" />
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "LegalService",
    "name": "Miao He — Notary Public Ontario",
    "url": "https://www.miaohelaw.ca/en/notary-public",
    "telephone": "+1-647-930-6688",
    "email": "miao@miaohelaw.ca",
    "address": {
      "@type": "PostalAddress",
      "streetAddress": "208-7050 Woodbine Ave",
      "addressLocality": "Markham",
      "addressRegion": "ON",
      "addressCountry": "CA"
    },
    "serviceType": ["Notary Public Ontario", "Document Notarization", "Certified True Copy", "Statutory Declaration", "Power of Attorney Notarization", "Mandarin Notary Services", "Chinese Document Certification Ontario"]
  }
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <HeaderEn />
  <main>
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="breadcrumb">
          <a href="/en/">Home</a> › Notary Public
        </div>
        <h1>Notary Public · Ontario</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">Mandarin &amp; English · Markham · 647-930-6688</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="container content-grid">
        <div class="main-content">

          <div class="definition-box">
            <p>Miao He is a commissioned <strong>Notary Public in Ontario</strong>, authorized to notarize documents for use in Canada and internationally. As a bilingual lawyer fluent in Mandarin and English, Miao He provides notary services without the need for an interpreter — ensuring accuracy and efficiency for Chinese-Canadian clients.</p>
          </div>

          <h2>Notary Services Available</h2>

          <div class="service-grid">
            <div class="service-item">
              <h3>Certified True Copies</h3>
              <p>Certified copies of passports, driver's licences, academic credentials, corporate documents, and other original documents.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-item">
              <h3>Statutory Declarations</h3>
              <p>Sworn written statements for immigration applications, financial institutions, government agencies, and legal proceedings.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-item">
              <h3>Affidavits</h3>
              <p>Sworn statements for use in court proceedings, family law matters, and administrative applications.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-item">
              <h3>Power of Attorney</h3>
              <p>Notarization of Powers of Attorney for use in Ontario and internationally, including for property transactions in China.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-item">
              <h3>Corporate Documents</h3>
              <p>Notarization of corporate resolutions, certificates of incumbency, and other business documents for domestic and international use.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-item">
              <h3>Documents for China</h3>
              <p>Notarization as a first step toward Apostille certification for documents to be used in China — coordinated with the full authentication process.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2>Why a Mandarin-Speaking Notary Public Matters</h2>
          <p>Notarization requires the notary to confirm the identity of the person signing and ensure they understand what they are signing. When the document is in Chinese or the client speaks Mandarin, using an English-speaking notary creates a communication gap that can cause errors, rejections, or legal complications. Miao He communicates directly in Mandarin — the notarization process is accurate and the client fully understands what they are signing.</p>

          <h2>Documents for Use in China</h2>
          <p>If you need Canadian documents authenticated for use in China — such as a Power of Attorney, a birth certificate, or a divorce order — notarization by a Notary Public is typically the first step before Global Affairs Canada certification and Apostille. Miao He handles the full process. See the <a href="/en/hague-apostille">Hague Apostille page</a> for more detail.</p>

          <div class="cta-box">
            <h3>Book a Notary Appointment</h3>
            <p>In-person at Markham office or by arrangement · Mandarin &amp; English · 647-930-6688</p>
            <a href="/en/contact" class="btn-primary">Book Now</a>
            <a href="tel:6479306688" class="btn-secondary">647-930-6688</a>
          </div>

        </div>

        <aside class="sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3>Contact Miao He</h3>
            <p>📞 <a href="tel:6479306688">647-930-6688</a></p>
            <p>📧 <a href="mailto:miao@miaohelaw.ca">miao@miaohelaw.ca</a></p>
            <p>📍 208-7050 Woodbine Ave, Markham</p>
            <p>💬 WeChat: 372656035</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3>Document Services</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><a href="/en/hague-apostille">Hague Apostille · China</a></li>
              <li><a href="/en/notary-public">Notary Public · Ontario</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3>Related Services</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><a href="/en/family-law/cross-border-assets">Cross-Border Asset Division</a></li>
              <li><a href="/en/family-law/domestic-contracts">Marriage Contracts</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3>Languages</h3>
            <p>🇨🇳 Mandarin (普通话)</p>
            <p>🇨🇦 English</p>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</body>
</html>
<style>
  .page-hero{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2C1810 0%,#4A2C1A 100%);color:white;padding:3rem 0 2rem}
  .page-hero h1{font-size:2rem;margin:0.5rem 0;color:#ffffff}
  .hero-sub{color:#D4A853;margin:0}
  .breadcrumb{font-size:0.85rem;opacity:0.7;margin-bottom:0.5rem}
  .breadcrumb a{color:white;text-decoration:none}
  .container{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.5rem}
  .content-section{padding:3rem 0}
  .content-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 300px;gap:3rem}
  .definition-box{background:#FDF6EC;border-left:4px solid #9A8060;padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;margin-bottom:2rem;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0}
  .service-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1rem;margin:1.5rem 0}
  .service-item{background:#f8f8f8;border-radius:8px;padding:1rem 1.2rem;border-left:3px solid #9A8060}
  .service-item h3{color:#2C1810;margin-top:0;font-size:0.95rem}
  .service-item p{margin:0.3rem 0 0;font-size:0.9rem;color:#4A2C1A}
  .cta-box{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2C1810,#4A2C1A);color:white;padding:2rem;border-radius:12px;text-align:center;margin-top:2rem}
  .cta-box h3{margin-top:0;color:#D4A853}
  .cta-box p{color:#ffffff}
  .btn-primary{display:inline-block;background:#D4A853;color:#2C1810;padding:0.75rem 1.5rem;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;margin:0.5rem}
  .btn-secondary{display:inline-block;background:transparent;color:white;border:2px solid white;padding:0.75rem 1.5rem;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;margin:0.5rem}
  .sidebar{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.5rem}
  .sidebar-card{background:white;border:1px solid #e8e0d5;border-radius:10px;padding:1.2rem}
  .sidebar-card h3{color:#2C1810;font-size:0.95rem;margin-top:0;border-bottom:1px solid #e8e0d5;padding-bottom:0.5rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem}
  .sidebar-card ul{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0}
  .sidebar-card li{padding:0.3rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0ebe3;font-size:0.9rem}
  .sidebar-card a{color:#9A8060;text-decoration:none}
  .sidebar-card p{margin:0.3rem 0;font-size:0.9rem}
  h2{color:#2C1810;margin-top:2rem}
  h3{color:#4A2C1A}
  @media(max-width:768px){.content-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.page-hero h1{font-size:1.5rem}.service-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
</style>
